 [M]FLD40REN(INDIC) = VALEUR
 Affzo FLD40REN(INDIC) : mkstat = 2
Endif
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_FLD40REN(zc) From W1ZBIC1
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_FLD40REN(zc) From W1ZBIC1
Onkey 144 Titled GBOUTP Call P_FLD40REN(zc) From W1ZBIC1
