## Action CTLDATVAL
Call CTLDATVAL(VALEUR,[M:BIC1]PERDEB) From CONTX3
If mkstat : GERR = 1 : GZONE = "PERFIN" : GZNUM = 978 : Endif
Gosub _AFF
End

